818ea975b53a7da5afdcf901468144c474681","tid":525354,"uid":106316,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T14:31:12.000Z","msg":"小二LV<br />\n答案就唔俾你喇<br />\n自已功課自已做<br />\n最多教你計<br />\n<br />\n19條左邊SET做x,底SET做y<br />\n用三個已知大小既三角形面積砌三條公式出黎<br />\n跟住S= xy-3-8-10就有答案<br />\n<br />\n20條普通解二次方程<br />\n冇咩特別"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"第20條得一條 binary quadratic equation<br />\n你試下普通咁解比我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我用partial derivative先計到<br />\n<br />\n第19條係易<br />\n但你中二果時識做？<br />\n我估你家下都要用幾十分鐘計"},{"pid":"d36f704ae99ca65a05ad2e1b018e114454ce375e","tid":525354,"uid":57675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T15:18:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小二LV<br />\n答案就唔俾你喇<br />\n自已功課自已做<br />\n最多教你計<br />\n<br />\n19條左邊SET做x,底SET做y<br />\n用三個已知大小既三角形面積砌三條公式出黎<br />\n跟住S= xy-3-8-10就有答案<br />\n<br />\n20條普通解二次方程<br />\n冇咩特別</blockquote>第20條得一條 binary quadratic equation<br />\n你試下普通咁解比我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我用partial derivative先計到<br />\n<br />\n第19條係易<br />\n但你中二果時識做？<br />\n我估你家下都要用幾十分鐘計</blockquote><br />\nEr...第20條應該唔洗partial D<br />\n佢話有solution<br />\n試下代x=某啲數 變成quadratic equation of y<br />\nCheck下b^2-4ac大唔大過零<br />\n咁就做到<br />\n(x,y)=(2,3)應該work 心算冇錯嘅話"},{"pid":"0b736215d434a808360d0a871b008f2bfbdac67a","tid":525354,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3a878f64a06bc5e2c48ee8f984787b8fbe608d","tid":525354,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d5357fe51a9d08623df7d1407fd7474f42222be","tid":525354,"uid":58609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"832818ea975b53a7da5afdcf901468144c474681","tid":525354,"uid":106316,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T14:31:12.000Z","msg":"小二LV<br />\n答案就唔俾你喇<br />\n自已功課自已做<br />\n最多教你計<br />\n<br />\n19條左邊SET做x,底SET做y<br />\n用三個已知大小既三角形面積砌三條公式出黎<br />\n跟住S= xy-3-8-10就有答案<br />\n<br />\n20條普通解二次方程<br />\n冇咩特別"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"第20條得一條 binary quadratic equation<br />\n你試下普通咁解比我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我用partial derivative先計到<br />\n<br />\n第19條係易<br />\n但你中二果時識做？<br />\n我估你家下都要用幾十分鐘計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"Let w,x,y,z be length of 左邊,左上,右上,右邊<br />\nwx=16,yz=6,(w-z)(x+y)=20<br />\n<br />\nwx-xz+yw-yz=20<br />\n16-xz+yw-6=20<br />\nyw-xz=10<br />\n<br />\n可以合理懷疑係整數解<br />\n(w,x) = (1,16),(2,8),(4,4),(8,2),(16,1)<br />\n(y,z) = (1,6),(2,3),(3,2),(6,1)<br />\n<br />\n然後reject頭尾<br />\n得返(w,x) = (8,2), (y,z) = (2,3)<br />\n<br />\n所以required area = 8*(2+2)-3-8-10 = 11"},{"pid":"fe56a28736cbf90ed9bc7ba4d4ad61dd7b0e79c9","tid":525354,"uid":106316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2d5357fe51a9d08623df7d1407fd7474f42222be","tid":525354,"uid":58609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"832818ea975b53a7da5afdcf901468144c474681","tid":525354,"uid":106316,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T14:31:12.000Z","msg":"小二LV<br />\n答案就唔俾你喇<br />\n自已功課自已做<br />\n最多教你計<br />\n<br />\n19條左邊SET做x,底SET做y<br />\n用三個已知大小既三角形面積砌三條公式出黎<br />\n跟住S= xy-3-8-10就有答案<br />\n<br />\n20條普通解二次方程<br />\n冇咩特別"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"第20條得一條 binary quadratic equation<br />\n你試下普通咁解比我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我用partial derivative先計到<br />\n<br />\n第19條係易<br />\n但你中二果時識做？<br />\n我估你家下都要用幾十分鐘計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T15:33:43.000Z","msg":"咪玩喇冇SIN COS <br />\n就咁用三角形面積SET 3條公式要幾十分鐘?<br />\n中二數LQ都唔會用幾十鐘做喇<br />\n何況係SQ<br />\n<br />\n20條叫你列幾對(x,y)<br />\n求其代D x=1,2,3.... y=1,2,3....<br />\n跟住解一元二次方程<br />\n唔係咁都唔識阿？"},{"pid":"c1b2417c58d5b6f193849bc21ce9cd9679d5a6b2","tid":525354,"uid":58609,"li