s://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Foi68.tinypic.com%2F2ufplpg.jpg&h=be443957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1/2*(16 + x)(1 - 6/x) = 10<br />\n<br />\nx^2 - 10x - 96 = 0<br />\n(x - 16)(x + 6) = 0<br />\n<br />\nx = 16"}]}